  '/images/tours/seoraksan-national-park/seoraksan-ridge-view.webp',
  '/images/tours/seoraksan-national-park/seoraksan-ridge-view.webp',
  'A 12-hour coach day trip from Seoul to the East Sea coast: hike Seoraksan National Park, visit the cliffside Naksansa Temple, and walk pine-backed Naksan Beach. Departs Mondays and Thursdays with an English-speaking guide and round-trip transfers from Hongik or Myeongdong.',
  'Gangwon-do Day Tour from Seoul: Seoraksan & Naksansa Temple | AtoC Korea',
